Description:
UNDER OFFER - Victoria Harbour Living with Scenic Park & Skyline Views
Boasting a wonderful easterly orientation which allows for beautiful Docklands Park views with Etihad Stadium and other buildings also in the distance, this smart and spacious two bedroom apartment offers a peace and tranquility that is so hard to find in living this close to the city.
The sensational central lounge and meals zone is defined by its open and sizeable layout, with the undercover balcony accessed via sliding doors from the main area and displays gorgeous tree views that will have a truly calming effect. The stone kitchen is also included in the lounge/meals hub and delivers stone surfaces, island bench and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher. The property has just been painted and carpeted throughout.
The bedrooms feature fabulous privacy separated by the sleek bathroom and both come with built-in robe storage. Other property features include a concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, video intercom, storage cage and secure car space.
Access a scenic community garden right next door, while you’re also close to The Hub @ Docklands, cafes and restaurants including Caffe Bambino, Cafenatics, The Merchant Society, and Banoi Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, Capital City Trail, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
To arrange an exclusive viewing please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304.

Work or Live at its Best! Super Spacious 1 Bedroom with 69sqm!
Private Inspections Welcome.
This super spacious 69sqm light filled and impressive one bedroom, is ideally situated in the heart of Docklands and the CBD with Etihad Stadium and transport literally at your door step, as well as Melbourne's heritage parks and gardens all within walking distance. You will also be positioned within walking distance to fabulous restaurants, cafes, shopping, entertainment and only moments to the centre of the CBD and Southbank. Other features include:
- a modern open plan kitchen with integrated appliances
- a contemporary style bathroom
- floor to ceiling windows flooding the living and dining area
- plenty of natural light
- air-conditioning/heating
- Secure intercom entry
- one secure undercover carspace

Description:
Light-Filled Luxury in Prestigious Palladio
Breathtaking harbour and stunning city views are all yours for the taking in this luxury 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the prestigious Palladio complex. Impeccably finished, distinctively detailed and wonderfully window-walled, discover a very real sense of space and depth in a property purpose-built for entertaining in style. This is privileged and prized Docklands living without care or compromise!
Sensationally staged sky-high on the 9th floor, discover a welcoming entrance hallway revealing the wide-reaching comforts of open-plan living and dining. A sleek, stone-topped kitchen features high-quality Smeg and Bosch appliances and an oversized breakfast bar, ideal for a Masterchef in the making. Entertain with substance on your choice of outdoor terraces showcasing city, bay and harbour vistas. The trio of carpeted bedrooms share terrace access, serviced by walk-in and built-in robes, a pair of fully tiled bathrooms (one with sumptuous bath), and a full-sized laundry. Prominently positioned, walk to Newquay Promenade restaurants, Docklands Stadium, the CBD, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station.
Packed with special features, enjoy secure side-by-side parking for 2 cars, panel heating, intercom entry, heated bathroom and resort-style facilities including pool, gym and BBQ terrace. This is truly living!

Description:
The Perfect Podium Residence
Dock 5, named after the sites original address, is the centre piece and the benchmark for what other residential apartments complexes are trying to strive for and emulate. Designed by multi award winning architect John Wardle, and predominantly owner occupied, Dock 5 has cemented its place as the go to apartment for buyers wishing to move to the area.
Available in the boutique plaza section of Dock 5 on level 6, this spacious two bedroom abode provides an exceptional residence.
Extra large dining and living area flows to a very generous full length balcony. From this location, the tranquil water aspect gives a perfect backdrop to view water vessels cruising past. Watch a ship glide by as the crew endeavour to capture the wind on their sails.
Back in the apartment, there is a chefs kitchen with all the stainless steel appliances required. Gas stove top, electric oven, convection/ microwave oven to go along with the upgraded Corian stone bench tops.
Master bedroom with walk through robe and ensuite, while second bedroom includes built in robes and shares the central stylish bathroom.
Other features include
• Reverse cycle ducted heating and cooling
• Security entrance, Intercom system
• Onsite manager
• New carpets
• Balcony Gas outlet for BBQ’s and water tap outlet
Recreation facilities consist of
• Indoor heated lap pool
• Gymnasium
• Communal BBQ area
Life is about balance, and as a reminder, John Wardle, who is renowned for this, has incorporated a cantilever component into the Dock 5. Being In the heart of the Docklands, what better way than for Dock 5 to provide perfect home and lifestyle.
Close to Woolworths, Post Office, Library at the Dock, fantastic cafes and eateries. Easy commute in and out. Free tram zoned. Short stroll to Southern Cross station and the freeway network.

Description:
Spacious, Sunny And So Well Positioned
As part of the exclusive Village Docklands complex and ready to impress all buyers with its generous and thoughtful floorplan, quality modern fittings and fixtures, and CBD views, this two bedroom + study, two bathroom apartment is residential excellence in the sought-after Batman’s Hill Precinct.
The entry flows into the ultra-spacious open living and dining zone, which has views to the east which take in the striking city buildings. These views can also be enjoyed from the long balcony where alfresco dining and drinks will be an easy option. The balcony is also accessed by both of the bedrooms.
The dazzling kitchen comes with a stone benchtop, mirrored splashback, and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher. Both bedrooms have plenty of robe storage options including the large master bedroom which promises a WIR and its own ensuite, meanwhile the bathroom is well-appointed and comes with a European laundry. Other highlights include a sizeable study or even 3rd bedroom option, split system heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a pool and BBQ courtyard.
You’re just a short walk or tram ride into the CBD, as well as being close to Collins Square, Docklands Park, Batman Park, Spencer Outlet Centre with eateries for lunches on the go, and Southern Cross Station.
To arrange an exclusive viewing, please contact Vicki Leong on 0452486860

Description:
A Yarra’s Edge marvel with space, style, and superb views
Located in the fantastic ‘Tower 5’ in the Yarra’s Edge precinct which sits just moments to all the action of South Wharf Promenade and DFO shopping, this tasteful and modern two bedroom apartment showcases a considered floorplan and two secure car spaces!
A sizeable undercover balcony has unique south-westerly views and will be your 2nd home during the warmer months as you enjoy drinks watching the sun setting in the distance. Inside, a sizeable lounge and dining zone is adjoined by a tiled stone kitchen complete with a moveable island bench and stainless steel Miele appliances.
Both bedrooms with mirrored built-in robes each boast fantastic privacy and are separated by the main living hub. Also benefit from a stylish double vanity bathroom, separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, 2 secure car spaces, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Walk to South Wharf with restaurants and bars including Meat Market, The Boatbuilders Yard, The General Assembly, and Plus 5 Bar. You’re also close to Crown Entertainment Complex, IGA supermarket, and public transport including Southern Cross Station and trams on Spencer Street.

Description:
Ultimate Refinement On The River
Inspect by Private Appointment this Saturday - Contact Gerald Betts 0418 371 855 to arrange a time.
Luxury free from limits, enhanced by Yarra's Edge Esplanade frontage, defines this substantial contemporary residence as a river-side address of peerless appeal. Light-filled spaces for living, dining and entertaining each open to elegant terraces that feature a barbeque bench and flow to down to the water while a kitchen equipped with Miele appliances includes a fitted coffee machine, integrated fridge and freezer and stylish storage. A living level powder room provides additional convenience. A dedicated study zone complements a design where four upstairs bedrooms and two bathrooms feature a seductive, spectacular main bedroom with a dressing room, stunning ensuite and balcony sights of the river and the city skyline. Below, four car garaging shares a fabulous basement level with a home theatre room, massive store room and substantial separate cellar. Home automation, heating/cooling, surround sound, CCTV security - the details beautifully match the big picture - completed by an allocated 18 metre marina berth (berth 179). Nothing could be better.

Description:
GRAND HERITAGE CHARM
The moment you enter the foyer you will be instantly taken by the magnificence of old world charm. Amid the 19th Century, Victorian architecture is this apartment. The discerning buyer can expect the very best of quality in this apartment located on the 1st Floor in Melbourne’s grandest building, brimming with charm and character. The building was originally built in 1893, and was refurbished in 1996 to accommodate a mix of serviced and residential apartments. The apartment features two bedrooms with brand new carpet, the master bedroom with built in robes and two-way bathroom, a well-appointed kitchen with quality appliances, generous bathroom and a vaulted ceiling height throughout. The living areas feature a large open plan lounge area adjacent to the kitchen and spacious meals area with timber floor boards and high ceilings perfect for entertaining. Services include an indoor swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, caretaker, BBQ area and tranquil gardens as well as the adjacent Piano Bar restaurant and cafe. Located only a stone’s throw away from all of the amenities the city of Melbourne has to offer including Southern Cross Station, Southbank promenade and the Crown Casino complex just to name a few. Don’t miss out on this luxurious apartment.
For a private inspection call Glenn Donnelly 0419 998 235

Description:
A premier and elite Docklands offering over 3 stunning floors
Situated in a peaceful pocket in the esteemed Yarra’s Edge precinct, and promising magnificent space and contemporary flair plus the addition of a huge entertainer’s deck which will be a dream for many summers to come, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom tri-level corner townhouse is a stunning opportunity.
This exceptional property features a first floor that is packed with amazing highlights. An open and carpeted lounge and dining zone feeds into the tiled kitchen area, which delivers stylish stone throughout including the island bench as well as stainless steel Miele appliances. This kitchen also has an adjoining casual meals space.
Flowing out from the kitchen is the completely private and superbly spacious entertainer’s deck, which will be able to host everything from large parties to BBQs with friends. Back inside and make your way to the top floor to take advantage of two extra-large bedrooms both with built-in robes, with the master bedroom also coming with a private ensuite. This top floor further offers a stylish bathroom.
The ground level adds some uniqueness to this property with an utterly expansive bedroom and living zone providing buyers standout flexibility. This huge space has its own entry from the side of the house, as well as access to a powder room, and could even be transformed into a large work space, studio, or even a gym! Other property features include ducted heating and cooling, European laundry, under stairs storage, secure alarm, and a remote double tandem garage.
You’ll never get tired of taking long strolls on the waterfront where you can soak in the wonderful views of the city in the distance, while there are plenty of green parks areas for you and your dog to enjoy. You’re also not far from South Wharf Promenade DFO Shopping, Capital City Trail, IGA X-Press supermarket, and the city with amazing attractions and transport.

Other property highlights include a well-appointed central bathroom with European laundry, separate study area for those who love working from home, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, and secure car space.
Enjoy Quays facilities which include a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, and a rooftop garden with BBQ and dining facilities.
Make the most of this excellent NewQuay Precinct position where you’re moments to Marvel Stadium, Central Pier restaurants including Mama Rumaan and Woolshed, an abundance of promenade restaurants, and trams on Harbour Esplanade.

Description:
Exclusive Sky Home with Uninterrupted Views
A rare offering of substantial distinction and unrivalled pedigree, this stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom entertainer offers an enticing world of luxury living with each and every space featuring enticing elements of timeless detail. Overlooking the city skyline, Victoria Harbour and Port Phillip Bay in a sweeping statement of style and sophistication, instantly click into relaxation mode on a pair of private terraces.
Spectacularly set on the 19th floor of the tightly held Nolan building, enjoy an impressive 121sqm of living space, complemented by a further 17sqm of external terraces (both approx.). Discover a welcoming entrance hallway branching off to a pair of large robed bedrooms united by access to a private balcony with breathtaking views of the Bolte Bridge. A luxurious bathroom services both these bedrooms, showcasing a marble-topped vanity, sumptuous bath and fully tiled shower.
Gentle textures and flowing lines define the interiors. A glistening, granite-topped Smeg kitchen boasting a super-stylish island bench pivots around a far-reaching, open-concept living and dining area. The main balcony is accessed from this point with 270 degree views on offer from the stunning city skyline to the river, marina, blue-water bay, the mountainous majesty of the Great Dividing Range, and the Melbourne Wheel. Grand in scale, the third bedroom shares in these views with a private entry point to the main balcony, dual-sided walk-in robes, and a striking marbled ensuite featuring a bathtub and fully tiled, walk-in shower.
Nothing has been left to chance with special features including a powder room, sleek tiling and plush carpets, a separate laundry with built-in cabinetry, ample storage, ducted heating and cooling, secure parking for 2 cars plus additional storage cage, video intercom entry, and exclusive access to resort-style facilities including a swimming pool and fully equipped gym.
You couldn't wish for a more convenient address. Walk to Newquay Promenade restaurants, Docklands Stadium, the CBD, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, free city trams, and Southern Cross Station. This is the life!

Description:
A Podium Finish
This tranquil low rise home with leafy green views provides the ideal residence.
The award winning Watergate residence, with its eye catching Aero dynamic design, is a standout in the heart of the Docklands
With a uniformed layout, this larger than normal one bedroom apartment utilises every nook and cranny with it’s well designed floor plan.
As you step into this West facing apartment you will appreciate the stylish kitchen with white stone benchtop and white cabinetry. Integrated stainless steel appliances include a gas stove top, oven and a dishwasher.
Open plan dining and living area adjoins the full length balcony set along lush greenery.
Large bedroom with mirrored BIR’s adjoins the stylish fully tiled bathroom with dual access.
Additional features include ducted reverse cycle heating and cooling, secured carpark, onsite manager with security entrance, floor to ceiling double glazed windows and cross flow ventilation.
Recreational facilities consist of a fantastic 3 lane heated swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a residents lounge.
Centrally located in the heart of the Docklands makes it convenience plus. Walking distance to Woolworths, Australia Post Office, Library at the Dock, Southern Cross Station, superb cafes and eateries. Free Tram Zoned, easy access to the freeway and a short stroll into Melbourne.
